    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 1.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_03-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "いらっしゃいませー！\n一日店長の、早坂芽衣だよー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Welcome!\nI'm Mei Hayasaka‚ the one-day manager!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.6774284601,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 8.2666667937
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_03-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣が考えた、にゃんこドーナツ\nめ～～いっぱい食べていってね～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please enjoy the cat donuts\nI created!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.2933180531,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 15.9333332061
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_03-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "お持ち帰りで、三つですね！\nありがとうございまーす！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Three to-go‚ right?\nThank you very much!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.4999998728,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 22.6666665394
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_03-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあチョコペンでドーナツの端に～\nめ～い、っと！　はい、どうぞ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now‚ let me use the chocolate pen to write on the edge of the donut~\nM-E-I‚ there you go!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.319358297,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_03-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "え～？　宝物にしちゃダメだよ～\nお早めにお召し上がりくださ～い！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ no! You don't have to keep it as a treasure!\nPlease enjoy it while it's fresh!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.9999998728,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 40.9833332061
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_03-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "実はキッチンでね、渚ちゃんと、トリエルのすみれ\nちゃんが、ドーナツを作るお手伝いしてるんだ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ in the kitchen‚ Nagisa-chan and Sumire-chan\nfrom TRINITYAiLE are helping make donuts!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.8999999682,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_03-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "夜のライブ、観に来てくれるの？\nありがとー！　ステージの上から探すね～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you coming to watch the live tonight?\nThank you! I'll look for you from the stage!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.8999998728,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 57.4666665394
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_03-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣さんのドーナツお渡し会\n大人気ですね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei-san's donut handout event is\nreally popular!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.7666665394,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 62.6666650134
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_03-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "チョコペンでドーナツにサインするなんて\n芽衣ちゃんらしい、面白いアイデアだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Signing the donuts with a chocolate pen is\nsuch a Mei-chan thing to do.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.1333332061,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_03-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "それに、お誕生日の日でも\nこうしてファンの人達と触れ合って、笑顔にして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And even on her birthday‚\nshe's interacting with fans and making them smile like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.5666665394,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 73.9999983468
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_03-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣さんも、疲れるどころか\nどんどん元気になってる気がしますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei-san doesn't seem to get tired at all.\nIn fact‚ she looks like she's getting more and more energetic.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.6666665394,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 79.5999983468
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_03-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "あ、そろそろ時間だし、私達も準備しよっか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ it's about time. Let's get ready.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.5999983468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 84.6333332061
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_03-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "お渡し会、楽しかった～～～～！\nもっともーっと続けたかったくらいだよー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The handout event was so much fuuun!\nI could have kept doing it even longer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.2999998728,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 266.66666680000617,
          "startTime": 85.9333332061
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 93.533333206
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_03-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "お店の人達も、お疲れ様でした\n本日はありがとうございました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks to the store staff as well‚ you all did a great job today.\nThank you very much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.8666665394,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_03-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "え？　芽衣も今日は店長だから、お店の人？\nえへへ、なんだか照れちゃうな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Since Mei is the manager today‚ does that make me store staff too?\nEhehe‚ it's a bit embarrassing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.1666665394,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 110.2666665393
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_03-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあそろそろ……あれ？\n渚ちゃん？　すみれちゃん？　雑誌の人達もいない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I guess it's about time to… Huh?\nNagisa-chan? Sumire-chan? The magazine people are gone too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.0333332061,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
