      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_03-mei012.m4a",
      "text": "メッセ……？\n「お店の外で待ってるね」……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A message…?\n\"We'll be waiting outside the store.\"",
