      "text": "（今日は楽しかったな～、渚ちゃんとすみれちゃん）\n（他にも、沢山の人にお祝いしてもらっちゃった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Today was so much fun. Nagisa-chan and Sumire-chan）\n（and so many other people celebrated with me.）",
